                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-24-18431127 t18431127-24-punishment-20"></join>Confined Six Months</rs>.—The first and last week Solitary.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Justice Coltman.</hi>
